:slide_title Humanoid Robots

:image :teslaoptimus, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px"}

**This is the Tesla Optimus, the humanoid robot**

* Tesla, Boston Dynamics, Amazon and others
* Cool Sci-Fi look
* Uncanny Valley
* What will it actually do?
* Humanoid robots like Tesla Optimus could perform dangerous or repetitive tasks, improving workplace safety for humans.
* These robots may provide companionship and social interaction for isolated individuals, potentially reducing loneliness in society.

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Surgical Robots

:image :davinci, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**The DaVinci Robot from Intuitive**

* Why is this consixered to be a robot?
* Allows certain kinds of surgeries to be more reliable
* They make big claims
* Surgical robots improve precision in complex procedures.
* They reduce recovery time for patients after surgery.

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Assistive Robots for the elderly

:image :companion, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Cognative Assisive Robots for Dementia Caree**

* Also look at [Jennie from Tombot](https://tombot.com)
* Allows certain kinds of surgeries to be more reliable
* Assistive robots can help older adults maintain independence and age in place comfortably.
* These robots can reduce the workload on caregivers and family members, improving their quality of life.

