:slide_title Autonomous public transportation systems

:image :airporttram, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Transportation between airport terminals**

* Autonomous public transport reduces traffic congestion.
* It improves accessibility for those unable to drive.
* There is no driver. It is autonomous?
* Would you consider it a robot?
* What if it were "smart"?

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Bomb Disposal Robots

:image :bomb, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Robots to safely examine suspicious packages**

* Dangerous situations where a robot can provide safety
* Usually a combination of remote control and autonomy
* [Many are "research projects" still](https://www.overtdefense.com/2020/11/26/re2-robotics-to-develop-autonomous-casualty-extraction-ugv-manipulator-arms-for-us-army/)
* Bomb disposal robots save lives of human technicians.
* They reduce the psychological stress on bomb squad personnel.

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Domestic Chore Robots

:image :roomba, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Roomba Autonomous Vaccum Cleaner**

* Well known product from [iRobot](https://www.irobot.com)
* I have two of them (a really old one and a somewhat old one)
* Overall assessment: they are a work saver
* Domestic chore robots free up time for family activities.
* They assist elderly or disabled individuals with daily tasks.

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Agricultural Robots

:image :agricultural, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Many different farm applications**

* This one is an experimental one from [Odd Bot Weedwhacker](https://www.odd.bot)
* Pulling weeds reduces the need for herbicides
* Greatly reduces the amoung of manual labor
* Agricultural robots increase crop yields and efficiency.
* They reduce the physical strain on farm workers.

<div style="clear:both; height:20px;"></div>

:slide_title Manufacturing Robots

:image :industrial, {class="float-right" style="margin-right: 30px; height:300px ;clear:right"}

**Robots used in manufacturing of all kinds**

* Utilizes advanced robotics technology from leading manufacturers.
* Increases production precision and reduces manufacturing errors.
* Significantly enhances production speed and output capacity.
* Improves workplace safety by handling hazardous tasks.
* Enables consistent 24/7 operation in manufacturing facilities.

